<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>UX/UI Internship Tasks</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="accordion-item active">
        <button class="accordion-header">
            <div class="left">
                <span class="number">1</span>
                <span class="title">Mobile App UX Case Study</span>
            </div>
            <span class="icon">⌄</span>
        </button>

        <div class="accordion-content">
            <h3>Goal</h3>
            <p>Design a complete UX case study for a mobile app.</p>

            <h3>Requirements</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>User research summary and personas</li>
                <li>User flows and wireframes</li>
                <li>High-fidelity prototype with 4-6 screens</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Deliverables</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Figma/Adobe XD link</li>
                <li>PDF summary</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-header">
            <div class="left">
                <span class="number">2</span>
                <span class="title">Website Landing Page UI Design</span>
            </div>
            <span class="icon">⌄</span>
        </button>

        <div class="accordion-content">
            <h3>Goal</h3>
            <p>Design a conversion-focused landing page for a product or service.</p>

            <h3>Requirements</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Wireframe + high-fidelity mockup</li>
                <li>Hero section, features, testimonials & CTA</li>
                <li>Typography and component specifications</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Deliverables</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Figma/XD design files</li>
                <li>Exported PNG screens</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-header">
            <div class="left">
                <span class="number">3</span>
                <span class="title">Design System & Component Library</span>
            </div>
            <span class="icon">⌄</span>
        </button>

        <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Create a design system with reusable UI components.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-header">
            <div class="left">
                <span class="number">4</span>
                <span class="title">Usability Testing & Iteration</span>
            </div>
            <span class="icon">⌄</span>
        </button>

        <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Conduct usability testing and improve the design.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
